---
import BaseLayout from '../../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import Breadcrumbs from '../../../components/Breadcrumbs.astro';
import { articleSchema, breadcrumbSchema } from '../../../lib/schema';

const title = 'Best Cordless Lawn Mowers 2026 - UK Ranked';
const description = 'Our pick of the best cordless lawn mowers for 2026. Five models ranked by performance, value and battery life from specs and verified owner reviews.';
const path = '/cordless-lawn-mowers/best/';
const datePublished = '2026-05-10';

const crumbs = [
  { name: 'Home', url: '/' },
  { name: 'Cordless lawn mowers', url: '/cordless-lawn-mowers/' },
  { name: 'Best 2026', url: path },
];

const schema = [
  breadcrumbSchema(crumbs),
  articleSchema({ headline: title, description, url: path, datePublished, dateModified: '2026-06-05' }),
].filter(Boolean);
---
<BaseLayout {title} {description} schema={schema} noindex={true} canonical="https://thebestmowers.co.uk/best-battery-powered-lawn-mower-reviews-uk/">
  <article class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 py-10">
    <Breadcrumbs items={crumbs} />

    <header class="mb-8">
      <p class="text-sm font-semibold text-grass-700 uppercase tracking-wide mb-2">Ranked List · Updated May 2026</p>
      <h1 class="text-3xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-soil-900 leading-tight">Best Cordless Lawn Mowers 2026</h1>
      <p class="mt-4 text-lg text-slate-700 leading-relaxed">
        Looking for the best cordless mower? Our fully ranked guide lives on the main reviews page, where we rank every model by cut quality, battery life and value with the full specs and owner feedback behind each pick.
      </p>
      <p class="mt-4">
        <a href="/best-battery-powered-lawn-mower-reviews-uk/" class="inline-flex items-center min-h-[44px] bg-grass-700 text-white font-semibold px-5 py-2 rounded-md hover:bg-grass-800">See the full ranked list &rarr;</a>
      </p>
    </header>

    <div class="prose-mowers">
      <h2>Our top five at a glance</h2>
      <ol>
        <li><strong>Gtech CLM 2.0</strong> - best for small to medium gardens. Light, stripes well, brilliant first mower. <a href="/reviews/gtech-clm50/" class="text-grass-700 underline">Full review</a> <a href="https://www.amazon.co.uk/s?k=gtech+clm50+lawn+mower&amp;tag=thebestmowers-21" rel="nofollow sponsored noopener noreferrer" target="_blank" class="text-grass-700 underline whitespace-nowrap">Check price &rarr;</a>.</li>
        <li><strong>Bosch UniversalRotak 36-550</strong> - best value if you're in the Bosch ecosystem. Huge grass box. <a href="/reviews/bosch-easyrotak-36-550-lawnmower/" class="text-grass-700 underline">Full review</a> <a href="https://www.amazon.co.uk/s?k=bosch+easyrotak+36+550+lawnmower+lawn+mower&amp;tag=thebestmowers-21" rel="nofollow sponsored noopener noreferrer" target="_blank" class="text-grass-700 underline whitespace-nowrap">Check price &rarr;</a>.</li>
        <li><strong>Ryobi RY18LMX40A</strong> - cheapest good cordless mower (bare tool under £160). <a href="/reviews/ryobi-cordless/" class="text-grass-700 underline">Full review</a> <a href="https://www.amazon.co.uk/s?k=ryobi+cordless+lawn+mower&amp;tag=thebestmowers-21" rel="nofollow sponsored noopener noreferrer" target="_blank" class="text-grass-700 underline whitespace-nowrap">Check price &rarr;</a>.</li>
        <li><strong>EGO LM2122E-SP</strong> - best for big gardens. Petrol-equivalent power. <a href="/reviews/ego-lm2122e-sp/" class="text-grass-700 underline">Full review</a> <a href="https://www.amazon.co.uk/s?k=ego+lm2122e+sp+lawn+mower&amp;tag=thebestmowers-21" rel="nofollow sponsored noopener noreferrer" target="_blank" class="text-grass-700 underline whitespace-nowrap">Check price &rarr;</a>.</li>
        <li><strong>Mountfield Princess 34 Li-48</strong> - best for stripes. Steel deck, proper roller. <a href="/reviews/mountfield-princess-34/" class="text-grass-700 underline">Full review</a> <a href="https://www.amazon.co.uk/s?k=mountfield+princess+34+lawn+mower&amp;tag=thebestmowers-21" rel="nofollow sponsored noopener noreferrer" target="_blank" class="text-grass-700 underline whitespace-nowrap">Check price &rarr;</a>.</li>
      </ol>

      <h2>Want more detail?</h2>
      <p>
        Our <a href="/cordless-lawn-mowers/" class="text-grass-700 underline">full cordless lawn mower guide</a> has a comparison table, buying advice and all the specs. We also have specialist guides:
      </p>
      <ul>
        <li><a href="/cordless-lawn-mowers/under-200/">Best cordless mowers under £200</a></li>
        <li><a href="/cordless-lawn-mowers/with-roller/">Cordless mowers with a rear roller</a></li>
        <li><a href="/cordless-lawn-mowers/large-gardens/">Cordless mowers for large gardens</a></li>
        <li><a href="/compare/cordless-vs-petrol/">Cordless vs petrol - which to buy</a></li>
      </ul>

      <h2>How we pick our best list</h2>
      <p>
        Our picks are built from manufacturer specifications, verified owner reviews on Amazon UK and retailer sites, and UK pricing data, cross-checked so the figures match the box. We rank on cut quality, battery and runtime for the garden size in question, weight with the battery fitted, noise and build quality. We review the list annually and drop anything discontinued or superseded.
      </p>
    </div>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>
